        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Freedom From Unnecessary Litigation Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a credit for the cost of insurance purchased to cover the costs of a negative outcome from surgery; and (2) exclude from gross income medical malpractice awards granted in binding arbitration.]]></text>
      </summary>
